# Pre-built Templates System

Templates are stored in `/src/renderer/src/data/templates` and provide ready-to-use card collections.

## Template Categories
Initial release includes 12 templates with 500+ cards:
- Beginner Words
- Small Talk
- Travel English
- Business English
- Advanced Vocabulary
- TOEFL Vocabulary
- Phrasal Verbs
- Idioms and Expressions
- Grammar Quick Tips
- Daily Routine Words
- Food & Restaurants
- Emergency English

## Template Structure
- Templates are JSON files containing deck data
- Each template follows the Deck interface structure
- Templates include metadata for categorization and display

## Template Guidelines
1. Maintain high-quality, curated content
2. Include clear context and examples
3. Follow consistent formatting
4. Support i18n where applicable
5. Version templates for updates

